All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.concurrent.Executor, java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService, java.util.concurrent.ScheduledExecutorService, org.openntf.domino.thread.XotsExecutorService
public class XotsDominoExecutor
extends org.openntf.domino.thread.DominoExecutor

Since:
1.0.0 Xots thread executor. ThreadPoolExecutor for Domino runnables. It sets up a shutdown hook for proper termination. There should be maximum one instance of DominoExecutor, otherwise concurrency won't work. Based on org.openntf.domino.xsp.xots.XotsDominoExecutor
Author:
Paul Withers
